<sect1 id="dir_b9cfb45c1b77dbd8e10a3c02853a7bae_1autotoc_md186">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::gamestate::listeners</title><para>Listeners for reacting to game state transitions.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b9cfb45c1b77dbd8e10a3c02853a7bae_1autotoc_md187">
<title>Listeners</title><para><table rows="3" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Listener  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Description  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>FocusMenuListener</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Focuses a menu when entering the Paused state  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>WorldResetListener</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Resets the game world on specific transitions  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b9cfb45c1b77dbd8e10a3c02853a7bae_1autotoc_md188">
<title>FocusMenuListener</title><para>Listens for transitions to the <computeroutput>Paused</computeroutput> state and sets focus to a configured menu. Clears focus when exiting the <computeroutput>Paused</computeroutput> state.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b9cfb45c1b77dbd8e10a3c02853a7bae_1autotoc_md189">
<title>WorldResetListener</title><para>Triggers a world reset on transitions such as:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Title → Running (game start)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Paused → Title (quit to menu)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Paused → Running (restart)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Running → Title (exit)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
